[32m│[0m logic)                                                                       [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ✅ Session-based multi-step flow architecture                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ✅ CSRF protection mechanism and cookie behavior                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ✅ Redirect behavior between steps                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ✅ No inline JavaScript or dynamically generated scripts affecting           [32m│[0m
