[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Confirmed XSS vulnerability with multiple successful payloads              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Clear evidence of unescaped user input in JavaScript context               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Reproducible across different XSS vectors                                  [32m│[0m
