[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m The username parameter from Step 1 is dynamically embedded in this           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m JavaScript alert, allowing XSS payloads to execute.                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
