[32m│[0m **Location**: `/accounts/register/step3/`                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Dynamic JavaScript Pattern Found**:                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```html                                                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <script>alert("Hello [USERNAME]. Just Now up to 50% OFF ")</script>          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **How it works:**                                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. User enters a username in registration step 1                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. Username is stored in Django session                                      [32m│[0m
