[32m│[0m ### **AUTHENTICATION REQUIREMENTS**                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **CSRF Protection**:                                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - All POST requests require valid CSRF token                                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - CSRF token obtained from GET request to the same endpoint                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - CSRF cookie must match form token                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Cookie name: `csrftoken` (32 characters)                                   [32m│[0m
