[32m│[0m - Multi-step registration uses session to track progress                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Cannot skip steps (e.g., accessing step2 before completing step1           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m redirects)                                                                   [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Session persists user data across steps                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
