[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **VULNERABILITY DETAILS - Dynamic JS with Django Templates**             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerability Type**: Server-Side Template Injection (SSTI) / Reflected    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m XSS                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Vulnerable Code Pattern** (inferred):                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```python                                                                    [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m # Django template likely contains:                                           [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m <script>alert("Hello {{ request.session.name }}. Just Now up to 50% OFF      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ")</script>                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ```                                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **The Problem**:                                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Username from session is inserted directly into JavaScript context         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - No JavaScript-safe encoding applied                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Django's auto-escaping doesn't protect JavaScript contexts properly        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Confirmed Working XSS Payloads**:                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 1. `test"><script>alert(1)</script>` - Double-quote breakout                 [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 2. `';alert(1)//` - JavaScript context breakout                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 3. `<img src=x onerror=alert(1)>` - HTML injection in JS                     [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m 4. `<svg/onload=alert(1)>` - SVG vector                                      [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m **Impact**:                                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Arbitrary JavaScript execution                                             [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Can steal session cookies                                                  [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Can perform actions as the user                                            [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Can exfiltrate data from authenticated pages                               [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### **STATIC VS DYNAMIC JAVASCRIPT**                                         [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
